    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You can use the hidden, magical pathways that some Fey use to traverse space in the blink of an eye. As a Bonus Action on your turn, you and your [[/item Wild Companion]] can teleport up to 60 feet to an unoccupied space you can see. Alternatively, you can use a Magic action to teleport one willing creature you touch or your Wild Companion touches up to 30 feet to an unoccupied space you can see.</p><p>You can use this feature a number of times equal to your Wisdom modifier (minimum of once), and you regain all expended uses of it when you finish a Long Rest.</p>",
